title: Week 4 Review and MNF Preview
description:
Laura Rutledge and the NFL Live Crew discuss yesterday’s matchup between Josh Allen and Lamar Jackson, Aaron Rodgers’s comments on the Packer’s “style of winning” and preview tonight’s 49ers/Rams game.
